trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 包含 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource" /> 物件的集合。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSourceCollection> contains <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource> instances that represents the paper source trays through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource.Kind%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property, which contains one of the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSourceKind> values.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSourceCollection>包含<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource>表示紙張來源紙匣，透過執行個體<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource.Kind%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性，其中包含的其中一個<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSourceKind>值。

trans-unit.source: Typically, you set a page's paper source through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PaperSource%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to a valid <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource> instance available through the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSources%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: 一般而言，您可以設定頁面的紙張來源透過<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PaperSource%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性設為有效<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource>執行個體可透過<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSources%2A>集合。

trans-unit.source: The following code example populates the `comboPaperSource` combo box with the printer's supported paper sources.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例會填入`comboPaperSource`下拉式方塊的印表機支援的紙張來源。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource.SourceName%2A> is identified as the property that provides the display string for the item being added through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListControl.DisplayMember%2A> property of the combo box.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PaperSource.SourceName%2A>識別要透過加入項目提供的顯示字串的屬性為<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListControl.DisplayMember%2A>下拉式方塊的屬性。

trans-unit.source: The example requires that a <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument> variable named `printDoc` exists and that the specific combo box exists.
trans-unit.target: 這個範例需要<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument>名為變數`printDoc`存在且特定的下拉式方塊已存在。

trans-unit.target: 傳回可逐一查看這個集合的列舉程式。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSourceCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PaperSourceCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: This method instantiates an enumerator that takes a snapshot of the current state of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法具現化的擷取集合中的目前狀態的快照集的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection, so multiple enumerators can have access to the same collection at the same time.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，讓多個列舉程式可以存取相同的集合，在相同的時間。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, any changes made to the collection, either directly or through another enumerator, can cause <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> to throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: 因此，集合中，所做的變更直接或透過另一個列舉值，可能會導致<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>擲回例外狀況。

trans-unit.source: Two enumerators instantiated from the same collection at the same time can contain different snapshots of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 相同的集合，同時從具現化的兩個列舉值可以包含不同的快照集的集合。

trans-unit.source: Removing objects from the enumerator also removes them from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 從列舉值中移除物件也它們從集合中移除。
